---
---

<section id="pricing" class="pricing">
  <div class="pricing-container">
    <div class="header-content animate-fade-up">
      <p class="subtitle">Investment</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Service Bundles</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Transparent pricing designed to flood your local business with leads.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- ROI Reality Check Anchor -->
    <div class="roi-anchor animate-fade-up">
      <p>💡 <strong>The ROI Reality Check:</strong> The average high-ticket service job is worth $500 - $1,500+. This means <strong>just ONE new client</strong> generated from this website instantly pays for your entire investment today. After that, it's pure profit.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <!-- Bundle 1 -->
      <div class="pricing-card animate-fade-up delay-100">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3>Google Maps Setup</h3>
          <p class="price"><span>$</span>299</p>
          <p class="desc">Dominate local search with a fully optimized Google Maps profile.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Complete Profile Optimization</li>
          <li>Local Keyword Strategy</li>
          <li>5-Star Review System Strategy</li>
          <li>Local Directory Citations</li>
          <li>Delivered in 3-5 Days</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://wa.me/61412345678" class="btn btn-secondary card-cta">Order Now</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Bundle 2 (Highlighted) -->
      <div class="pricing-card highlighted animate-fade-up delay-200">
        <div class="card-badge">Most Popular</div>
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3>Website + Google Maps</h3>
          <p class="price"><span>$</span>599</p>
          <p class="desc">The ultimate package for a powerful and visible online presence.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Everything in Website Package</li>
          <li>Complete Google Maps Setup</li>
          <li>Advanced Local SEO Strategy</li>
          <li>Review Generation System</li>
          <li>Priority 7-Day Delivery</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://wa.me/61412345678" class="btn btn-primary card-cta">Order Now</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Bundle 3 -->
      <div class="pricing-card animate-fade-up delay-300">
        <div class="card-header">
          <h3>Website Only</h3>
          <p class="price"><span>$</span>399</p>
          <p class="desc">A high-performance, conversion-optimized landing page or portfolio.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="features">
          <li>Lightning-Fast Custom Code</li>
          <li>Mobile-First Design</li>
          <li>Integrated Quote/Booking Form</li>
          <li>Free Premium Hosting ($0/yr)</li>
          <li>On-Page Local SEO Setup</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://wa.me/61412345678" class="btn btn-secondary card-cta">Order Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Add-On Banner (Maintenance) -->
    <div class="addon-banner animate-fade-up delay-300">
      <div class="addon-content">
        <h3>Ongoing Maintenance & Updates (Optional)</h3>
        <p>Because I build blazing-fast custom websites (no clunky WordPress dashboards), I handle all the updates for you. Need to change a photo or update text? Just WhatsApp me. It's done within 24 hours.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="addon-price">
        <span class="price-val">$99</span>
        <span class="price-period">/month</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Guarantee Banner -->
    <div class="guarantee-banner animate-fade-up delay-400">
      <div class="guarantee-icon">🛡️</div>
      <div class="guarantee-content">
        <h3>100% Risk-Free Guarantee</h3>
        <p>I know it's hard to trust a new marketing partner. That's why for your first website project, you pay <strong>$0 upfront</strong>. I'll build it, and you only pay the invoice if you absolutely love it and want to launch it. If not, we walk away as friends. No risk, just results.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    background-color: var(--color-cream);
    color: var(--color-dark-blue);
  }

  .pricing-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .header-content {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--color-accent-blue);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-dark-blue);
  }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  /* ROI Anchor */
  .roi-anchor {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
    background-color: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
    border-left: 4px solid #16a34a;
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .roi-anchor p {
    color: var(--color-dark-blue);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .roi-anchor p strong {
    color: #16a34a;
  }

  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .pricing-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
  }

  /* Highlighted Card */
  .pricing-card.highlighted {
    background-color: var(--color-dark-blue);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    transform: scale(1.05);
    border: none;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.15);
  }

  .pricing-card.highlighted:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05) translateY(-5px);
  }

  .card-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -15px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background-color: var(--color-accent-blue);
    color: white;
    padding: 6px 20px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .card-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.1);
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .pricing-card.highlighted .card-header {
    border-bottom-color: rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.1);
  }

  .card-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: inherit;
  }

  .price {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .price span {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .currency {
    font-size: 1rem !important;
    margin-top: 2rem !important;
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
    color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.5);
  }

  .pricing-card.highlighted .currency {
    color: rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.5);
  }

  .desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .pricing-card.highlighted .desc {
    color: rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.8);
  }

  .features {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .features li {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .pricing-card.highlighted .features li {
    color: rgba(249, 246, 240, 0.9);
  }

  .features li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent-blue);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .pricing-card.highlighted .features li::before {
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .btn {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--color-dark-blue);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-dark-blue);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-dark-blue);
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background-color: var(--color-accent-blue);
    color: #ffffff;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent-blue);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    color: var(--color-dark-blue);
    border-color: #ffffff;
  }

  /* Addon Banner */
  .addon-banner {
    background-color: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.02);
  }

  .addon-content h3 {
    color: var(--color-dark-blue);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .addon-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .addon-price {
    background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    color: var(--color-accent-blue);
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0;
    text-align: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .price-val {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .price-period {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* Guarantee Banner */
  .guarantee-banner {
    background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05);
    border: 1px dashed var(--color-accent-blue);
    border-radius: 0;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .guarantee-icon {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .guarantee-content h3 {
    color: var(--color-dark-blue);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .guarantee-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .pricing-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
    }
    .pricing-card.highlighted {
      transform: none;
    }
    .pricing-card.highlighted:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    .addon-banner {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pricing {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
    .pricing-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }
    .price {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    .guarantee-banner {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
